com.mia.umlmia.generalmechanisms
Interface UMLPackage

All Superinterfaces:
java.lang.Comparable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, com.mia.openapi.MIAEvaluableObject, com.mia.openapi.MIAObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, UMLGeneralizableElement, UMLMIAObject, UMLModelElement, UMLPackage
All Known Subinterfaces:
UMLModel, UMLSubsystem
public interface UMLPackage
extends UMLGeneralizableElement, UMLPackage

A representation of the model object 'UML Package'.

The following features are supported:

  • Owned Classifiers
  • Owned Associations
  • Imported Classifiers
  • Imported Packages
  • Imported In Packages
  • Package
  • Owned Packages

See Also:
